data.text:
About our Office

The Collin County office opened in 2021 in the firm’s largest geographic expansion to date with the Dallas and San Antonio offices opening at the same time. The office houses the estate planning group for the north Texas region and the Tax/IRS practice group.

The office supports many industry groups and non-profit charitable organizations in the area such as the Dallas Estate Planning Counsel, the Texas Trust Bankers Association, Communities Foundation of Texas, Make a Wish Foundation of North Texas, and the Dallas Arboretum and Botanical Garden.
